{
  "stem": "2165.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So my sister was in that group, and after she got herself settled in that room, she sent two men at night.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "At that Saturday when we went out for the water, they came, took me to her place, and we joined together.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were notified by a message through the chimney.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, a few days before I left, we knew already that-- in the beginning, the German used to clean up the house, then they start searching for people.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we heard them already searching, and we knew less and less and less food is coming in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we had messages through pieces of paper that-- that so much they can help, and the camp is disappearing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was notified to wait.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That Saturday when they open up to go for water, I will be taken to my sister.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I came there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They washed me up, and then they put me in another room.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I was with my sister, and it was one room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We all lived in one room.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And once a day--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was the youngster.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was only 13 and a half.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mostly were people over 18, because they couldn't work in the camp, because they were less than 18.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was the only child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mostly there were people from-- from 19 to-- to probably to late-- mid-40s, something.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably those people work in the camp, and they made arrangement through-- you know, one probably knows the other, and through that-- through that Commandant from the camp.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He-- and whoever had money paid.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
